r.s: Provides extra data structures and iterable/array functionality.
r.d: teds (Tentative Extra Data Structures) is a collection of data structures and iterable functionality
r.n: * Add `StableSortedListSet` and `StableSortedListMap` as memory-efficient alternatives to `SortedStrictSet`/`SortedStrictMap`. * Speed up `SortedStrictSet::__unserialize` and `SortedStrictMap::__unserialize` when data is already sorted. * Fix crash in `StrictSet` and `SortedStrictSet` during cyclic garbage collection.
